Program: Discovery
Title: Life Cycles - time and health
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrytq
Last Broadcast Date: 25 November 2004
How working against the body's natural body clock can cause problems. How going with the rhythms of life is important. Shift workers, and those who work against the body's natural pulse, have poorer health than others - and experience more accidents.